snippet.title: Cuit - A challenging and relaxing puzzle game | Trailer
snippet.description:
Cuit is a minimalistic and challenging puzzle game for Windows, Android and iOS. If you like being challenged, this is the right game for you. 
Steam:
        http://store.steampowered.com/app/614890/Cuit/
Website:
